                    <strong>Lottery odds are calculated live from the current NBA standings.</strong> The 14 teams with the worst records compete for the top 4 picks. Odds are assigned by the official NBA lottery structure — teams with worse records get more combinations.
                    <br><br>
                    Picks 5–14 are awarded in reverse order of record to the remaining lottery teams. The Sixers' odds update <strong>automatically each day</strong> based on current W-L record.
                </div>

